CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: Metals Acquisition Limited (MTAL) is a company focused on operating and acquiring metals and mining businesses in high quality, stable jurisdictions that are critical in the electrification and decarbonization of the global economy. The Company completed its first acquisition with the purchase of the CSA copper mine in Australia from Glencore PLC in June 2023.
